{"word":"G2693 - καταστρώννυμι - katastrṓnnymi - kat-as-trone'-noo-mee - Overthrow","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταστρώννυμι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katastrṓnnymi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-as-trone'-noo-mee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Overthrow</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அழிக்கப்படு"},{"paragraph":"to strew over (the ground); to prostrate, slay"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G4766 - στρώννυμι - strṓnnymi - strone'-noo-mee/4766\">G4766</a>; to <i>strew down</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>prostrate</i> (<i>slay</i>): - overthrow.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}